{"type": "article", "id": 13293, "title": "屋顶天窗的正确打开方式？这里有几个来自伦敦和日本的例子", "description": "不过这些设计都很难在贵国实现啊。", "date": "2015-08-11T12:05:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 14284, "name": "建筑物采光"}, {"id": 14285, "name": "天窗"}, {"id": 14286, "name": "天台"}, {"id": 14006, "name": "住宅设计"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 101, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702122444oq9N6zJORxZ54ean.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t房子的天窗要怎么开才合适？一对伦敦的年轻夫妇邀请设计机构 <a href=\"http://scenarioarchitecture.com\" target=\"_blank\">Scenario Architecture </a>为自家房子设计一个天窗，他们希望能观察到两个孩子在天台上的活动。天窗一方面增加了室内的光线，另一方面拓展了家长的视野，他们能随时看到天台上玩耍的孩子们。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<em> </em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122437tgvWPIVGD3b5okqF.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"457\" title=\"凹陷的部分被设计成了一个天窗\" alt=\"凹陷的部分被设计成了一个天窗\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>凹陷的部分被设计成了一个天窗</span> </em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122438K8JEHyT9FoW4O7QP.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"457\" title=\"家长们能随时观察到孩子在天台上的活动\" alt=\"家长们能随时观察到孩子在天台上的活动\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>家长们能随时观察到孩子在天台上的活动</span> </em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122438CvTxIkhg7L8dXroJ.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"457\" title=\"另一个角度看天窗\" alt=\"另一个角度看天窗\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>另一个角度看天窗</span> </em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122439aqC0R4O2yoVXUL5B.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"457\" title=\"设计风格温馨清爽\" alt=\"设计风格温馨清爽\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>设计风格挺清爽</span></em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122439hBDkA9JemKvz51wo.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"457\" title=\"两个娃\" alt=\"两个娃\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>两个娃</span></em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122440Wu7L6e1MRZngDoNx.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"457\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></em>\r\n</p>\r\n<em>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122440E2cpgBukN1oy4VLZ.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"457\" title=\"阅读室\" alt=\"阅读室\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>阅读室</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122441qeU690nfrvmcQkMb.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"457\" title=\"卧室的样貌\" alt=\"卧室的样貌\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>卧室长这样</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122441y1qSb0PsLH6AelMX.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"457\" title=\"天台\" alt=\"天台\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>天台</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122442oSpi7fXVxBbqHF4k.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"457\" title=\"另一个角度看天台\" alt=\"另一个角度看天台\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">另一个角度看天台。2013 <span>年，<a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2013/04/16/nn-house-by-kozo-yamamoto/\" target=\"_blank\">有个日本建筑师也使用过这种天窗</a>，且业主也是一个有孩子的家庭。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122442Ke4BvAX6Rxn7Hzc5.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"457\" title=\"黑色的窗框\" alt=\"黑色的窗框\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>黑色的窗框</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122443bMm9n2HyRhx7d5vS.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"457\" title=\"内室效果\" alt=\"内室效果\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>内室效果</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122443Sb1JHlciZjy0wm7f.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"457\" title=\"内室的另一个角度\" alt=\"内室的另一个角度\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>内室的另一个角度</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021224441MzvVDaJCQ2mOTc9.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"457\" title=\"倾斜的围墙\" alt=\"倾斜的围墙\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>倾斜的围墙</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n</em> \r\n<p>\r\n\t<em>题图来源：</em><a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2015/08/08/scenario-architecture-london-fields-apartment-sunken-roof-terrace/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>dezeen</em></a>\r\n</p>\n\n"}